But be it so, that I am not able to translate thus;
as he had neede to be a good Grecian who should translate
in such manner: what then should I do?

I haue heard moreouer of all the Radices, with their Primitiue
significations alone, drawne into a very little space;
which being well performed, must needes be a notable furtherance.

By this helpe they will be able to vnderstand, and make
